@arg? animate [Boolean]
  @description
    Whether or not to animate the collapsible state transition. The default
    is true - which means animation will be used.

  @default: true
    @removed 0.13.0
      @description
        The default is now determined by @code[options.animate]

  @default: The value passed in as the @code[animate] option in the constructor
    @added 0.13.0
